# Game Card KPI Removal Patterns

## Overview
This rule documents the successful removal of ROAS and Install KPI metrics from game cards across the AppSamurai Dashboard.

## Components Affected
The following components were modified to remove KPI metrics from game cards:

### 1. Dashboard Component
- **File**: [src/components/Dashboard.tsx](mdc:src/components/Dashboard.tsx)
- **Sections**: Customers and Account Managers tabs
- **Changes**: Removed grid layout showing installs and ROAS D7 metrics

### 2. FileManager Component  
- **File**: [src/components/FileManager.tsx](mdc:src/components/FileManager.tsx)
- **Location**: Main page game cards display
- **Changes**: Removed metrics grid showing totalInstalls and avgRoasD7

## Implementation Pattern

### Before (KPI Metrics Present)
```typescript
<div className="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 items-end">
  <div className="text-center">
    <div className="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">
      {game.totalInstalls.toLocaleString()}
    </div>
    <div className="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Installs</div>
  </div>
  <div className="text-center">
    <div className="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-400">
      {(game.avgRoasD7 * 100).toFixed(1)}%
    </div>
    <div className="text-xs text-muted-foreground">ROAS D7</div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### After (KPI Metrics Removed)
```typescript
<div className="text-center text-xs text-muted-foreground">
  {game.dateRange.start} - {game.dateRange.end}
</div>
```

## Game Card Structure (Post-Removal)
Game cards now display only:
- **Game Name**: Prominent title with platform badges
- **Date Range**: Centered date range display
- **View Game Button**: Action button to navigate to detailed view

## Critical Rules
- ✅ Never display totalInstalls or avgRoasD7 metrics on main page game cards
- ✅ Keep game cards clean and focused on essential information only
- ✅ Maintain "View Game" button for detailed performance access
- ✅ Preserve date range information for context
- ✅ Test both Dashboard and FileManager components when making changes
- ✅ Verify changes on production site after deployment

